<br>
It is no longer my place to speak here, though I will as oft I am seen as overstepping my bounds anyway.  I do however claim a right as Our Lord and Master has not as yet removed his Hate from my heart.  I still am a tiller...do any of you deny this?  Do even the highest of you dare to gainsay he Mighty Lord Innoruuk?  I didnt think so.  I am sent as a spy out into the world of the light but am cut off from my fellows of Hate.<br>
Why will none of you speak with me any longer?  You think I have fallen from the Grace of our Lord?<br>
<br>
Ask the Mad One if he thinks this is true.<br>
<br>
For now I ask that you consider carefully letting any rangers into the guild Halls except the chosen Hound of Innoruuk.  <br>
<br>
I am the Dire Wolf of Innoruuk and I have spoken!!!!<br>
<br>
